data.description: This property has a private setting and ideal location nestled on over 10 acres of a wooded backdrop with a large pond across the street. This 4+Bedroom, 4.5 Bath home features pure elegance and accessibility for those in need of main floor everything!  A stunning foyer with a loft above opens to a formal DR and an office on each side. The kitchen has granite counters with a center island and glass doors to a private patio. The great room features a FP with stone surround and leads to fabulous main floor Primary ensuite with vaulted ceilings, walls of windows and the largest tiled shower you have seen. Upstairs are 3 large bedrooms each with attached baths and a loft. The LL boasts a 2nd kitchen, exercise room and expansive rec area. Stunning park-like setting with ponds, parks and privacy
